Real Foil | Simple Typography Modern Photo Wedding Foil Invitation

Best Deals! Real Foil | Simple Typography Modern Photo Wedding Foil Invitation – weddings This item is trending! Real Foil It’s a great choice Real Foil See more about itAdd some shine to your wedding invitations with real gold, silver, or rose gold foil! This classic and timeless metallic style is sure to add another level to your invites. These luxurious invitations make a great impact with real pressed foil. Incorporating foil-stamped elements on luxe paper is a perfect way to set the tone for your celebration. This simple, elegant modern photo wedding invitation features your engagement photo at the top of the page with a foil frame. Your names and date details appear in real pressed foil underneath. Cards reverse to the wedding invitation text with all your event details in a stylish serif and script lettering typography. We have chosen two template photos with a boho desert color scheme of neutral earthy sand tones, but the classic black and white color scheme of the typography is sure to match any wedding colors. You can customize this design to feature your wedding colors or you might choose to change the fonts, foil colors, punctuation, or placement used for various text elements of this design on the front and/or back. The photos can be replaced with your own, if you only want to showcase one photo, the reverse can be deleted to uncover a classic white background. To access these advanced editing options, simply click on "Personalize" and "Edit using Design Tool". If you need a hand with something or would like to work with me on a custom order, feel free to message me through the button below!
